 340:src/voice.h   **** // ŌöĆŌöĆ Voice 4: clean sine organ / flute (a melodic, non-bass departure) ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌö
 341:src/voice.h   **** //   Pure sine oscillators stacked like organ drawbars: octave-down body, root,
 342:src/voice.h   **** //   octave-up air, plus a second osc tuned a hair sharp (1.005├Ś) for a slow,
 343:src/voice.h   **** //   warm chorus shimmer instead of a chord. Higher register than the basses, a
 344:src/voice.h   **** //   mostly-open clean filter, and just a touch of drive so pressure adds gentle
 345:src/voice.h   **** //   harmonic warmth. Sines never alias, so it stays smooth all the way up.
ARM GAS  /tmp/claude-502/cceToCIK.s 			page 44


